<h1> Napowrimo 2020 Day 8 - Stagecraft </h1>
<p><i>Published on: <time datetime="2024-07-16T10:34:16.702Z">July 16, 2024</time></i></p>
    
       <a href="/posts/tag/posts">#posts</a>
    
       <a href="/posts/tag/poetry">#poetry</a>
    
	<br>
<p>What is going on? I ask the<br>
walls every sixteen minutes.<br>
The plasterboard doesn't reply<br>
but without checking headlines</p>
<p>I know clouds are being pulled<br>
across the sky on invisible<br>
ropes. Right on cue, rain is<br>
directed through pipes to fall.</p>
<p>Powered by vast hidden engines,<br>
the waves are continuing their<br>
metronome beat upon the sand.<br>
Blooms are raised from trapdoors</p>
<p>and some complex set of gears,<br>
ball bearings and levers is causing<br>
our planet to spin forward and new<br>
universes to be created every second.</p>
<hr>
<p>Prompt was &quot;Ask and answer a question&quot; from <a href="https://www.instagram.com/amykaypoetry/">AmyKayPoetry</a></p>

